Class ComposedMapper<C,I,O>

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DesMapper<I,O>, PsSetter<O>, RsGetter<O>, SerMapper<I,O>

    public class ComposedMapper<C,I,O>
extends Mapper<C,I,O>
    This is the primary concrete field mapper implementation. A type-safe mapper for a specific field of a given class.
